    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and is being sold as a reliable but well-used daily driver. The exterior shows its age with several noticeable scratches, minor fading in the clear coat on the roof, and a few small door dings. Inside, the upholstery has some visible wear and a small tear on the driver's seat bolster, though all electronics remain functional. Mechanically, the car runs and drives well, but it will likely need a suspension refresh and new tires in the near future. This is a solid option for someone looking for a functional vehicle who doesn't mind some cosmetic imperfections and minor upcoming maintenance.",
