    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You have got to see this absolute beauty! I\u2019ve treated this car like my own baby, and it\u2019s honestly in such incredible shape it still has that 'new car' feel. It's been kept spotless, garaged every single night, and runs like a total dream. If you're looking for a ride that's basically perfect and ready for its next adventure, you\u2019ve found it! I'm so excited for someone to get behind the wheel and love it as much as I have. Drop me a message and come check it out!",
      "price": 43500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
