      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 49
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_8_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_8",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a superlative example of the S54-powered legend, presented in collector-grade condition. The high-revving 3.2L inline-six features meticulously maintained individual throttle bodies and a refreshed dual-VANOS system, delivering surgical throttle response and linear power to the 8,000 RPM redline. Critical preventative maintenance has been addressed, including documented rod bearing replacement and comprehensive rear subframe reinforcement for enhanced structural rigidity. The drivetrain features the sought-after Getrag 6-speed manual transmission, offering crisp, tactile shifts mated to a variable M-differential lock. The chassis remains taut, preserving the communicative steering rack and balanced 50/50 weight distribution that defines the platform. Every panel gap is factory-perfect and the undercarriage is free of oxidation, reflecting a life of climate-controlled storage and obsessive mechanical stewardship.",
      "price": 44500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 49
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_3",
