    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "Presenting a truly showroom-quality vehicle that has been fastidiously maintained by a single enthusiast owner. The exterior features original, high-gloss paint with zero swirl marks or rock chips, further preserved by a professional-grade ceramic coating. Inside, the cabin is indistinguishable from new; the premium leather remains supple and matte, free of any bolster wear or creasing, and it has never been smoked in. Mechanically, this car is flawless, with a comprehensive service history binder showing all maintenance performed ahead of schedule at authorized service centers. It has been strictly garage-kept under a breathable cover and has never seen rain or snow. Every feature, from the infotainment to the heated seats, functions perfectly. This sale includes both original keys, the window sticker, all owner\u2019s manuals, and a set of pristine factory floor mats. This is a rare opportunity to own a collector-grade example that satisfies even the most rigorous inspection.",
